reviewText: i first saw this at 1 a.m. on television in steubenville ohio and could not believe my eyes and ears...rossi's rock music, with exorcism footage...it was so gripping, so surrealistic...so amazing....his closing song "jesus is my song" is amazing!!!
... Five Stars!... A cinematic masterpiece capturing on tape for the first time healings and exorcisms like we read in the gospels!!
